OP of Anime "Magic of Stella"（ステラのまほう）
Notes: 386
Difficulty: 23
It's my 3rd chart!
At first, I wanted to make a LV.25+ chart but I failed because making a LV.25+ chart of this song will make the chart a mess. I only made a chart which difficulty is 23(or maybe lower).
HimariPout
By the way, the anime "Magic of Stella" is a wonderful anime but it enjoys a low popularity. Strongly suggests to have a try watching that.
If you like my charts, please subscribe me. I'll keep posting new charts.
And if you want me to make a chart of your favorite song, tell me in the comment area and I'll try to make that.
And if there are any problems in my chart, please tell me in the comment area too.
